  "detailed_description": "<h1>ADD ELON TO WISHLIST</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1120920/extras/32f9bf274be5270cdfbc1ada1faa123d.poster.avif?t=1569233940\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1120920/extras/32f9bf274be5270cdfbc1ada1faa123d.webm?t=1569233940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1120920/extras/32f9bf274be5270cdfbc1ada1faa123d.mp4?t=1569233940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > ELON on MARS </h2> is the next Big Step game for our generation. Not only have we reached the Mars, but we also got a bit of “stuff cleaning” to do..<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1120920/extras/4953e4f7fc592f995c6b55ed0ab55ac8.poster.avif?t=1569233940\" width=600 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1120920/extras/4953e4f7fc592f995c6b55ed0ab55ac8.webm?t=1569233940\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1120920/extras/4953e4f7fc592f995c6b55ed0ab55ac8.mp4?t=1569233940\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > ELON on MARS </h2> is all about Mars General Cleaning! Get rid of excessive amount of space objects flying around this cool planet by shooting them down. Different space objects cause you different level of injury so.. be aware.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>dynamic space shooter mechanics<br></li><li>variety of danger on your way<br></li><li>truly Mars-ish aura & environment </li></ul>",
